    <s:String x:Key="LabelTriggerKey">触发按键</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="DescTriggerKey">输入自定义按键名称 (如: MiddleMouse, XButton1, F1, F2 等)，或点击"监听"按钮按下任意键</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="BtnListen">监听</s:String>
    <s:String x:Key="BtnListenTip">点击后按下任意键将其设为触发键</s:String>
